chart_description: This chart displays the percentage of time the IO subsystem is under some pressure, where some pressure means that at least one task is waiting for IO to complete.

dimension_descriptions.some 10: The chart shows the percentage of time the IO subsystem was under some pressure during the 10s interval.
dimension_descriptions.some 300: The chart shows the percentage of time the IO subsystem was under some pressure during the 5min interval.
dimension_descriptions.some 60: The chart shows the percentage of time the IO subsystem was under some pressure during the 1min interval.
